"title": "5442: pilgrimage",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5442",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A journey made to a holy or revered place as an act of devotion or duty. As well as Jerusalem, there were several such holy places in Israel.</p>\n<h2>The annual pilgrimages</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:23-Exod34:24\">EXO 34:23–34:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:41-Luke2:42\">LUK 2:41–2:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:14\">EXO 23:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:17\">EXO 23:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:16\">DEU 16:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:11\">DEU 31:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:2-2Chr5:3\">2CH 5:2–5:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:1\">2CH 30:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:13\">2CH 30:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:4\">LAM 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:9\">EZK 46:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:16-Zech14:19\">ZEC 14:16–14:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:1\">JHN 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:14\">JHN 7:14</a></p>\n<h2>Pilgrimages to Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps122:1-Ps122:4\">PSA 122:1–122:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:5\">PSA 84:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:3\">ISA 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:29\">ISA 30:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:2\">MIC 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:5-Acts2:11\">ACT 2:5–2:11</a></p>\n<h2>Accompanying sacrifices</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:27-1Kgs12:28\">1KI 12:27–12:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:12\">ISA 1:12</a></p>\n<h2>Other centres of pilgrimage</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:3\">1SA 1:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:4\">1KI 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:26-1Kgs12:30\">1KI 12:26–12:30</a></p>\n<h2>Used metaphorically</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:9\">GEN 47:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:13-Heb11:16\">HEB 11:13–11:16</a></p>",
